step_data.thought: I'm now on the 'Import group' page. Looking at the page structure, I can see that there are two main ways to import a group: 1) Import from another GitLab instance by providing credentials, or 2) Import from a file. Since the goal specifically mentions importing from another GitLab instance, I should use the first method. To do this, I need to fill out the 'GitLab source URL' field first. This field has BID '365'.
